        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued July 18 at 1:29PM MDT by NWS Great Falls MT</headline>
        <description>At 128 PM MDT, Doppler radar was tracking a cluster of strong
thunderstorms along a line extending from 17 miles west of Divide
Lake to 9 miles southwest of Lima. Movement was east at 25 mph.

HAZARD...Wind gusts up to 50 mph.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Gusty winds could knock down tree limbs and blow around
unsecured objects.

Locations impacted include...
Lima, Dell, Cameron, and Snowline.
</description>
        <instruction>If outdoors, consider seeking shelter inside a building.</instruction>
